    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've got to check out this absolute stunner. It is in truly mint condition\u2014I\u2019ve honestly babied this car from day one, and it still has that fresh, like-new feel! It drives like an absolute dream and looks even better in person. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been meticulously cared for and is ready for its next adventure, this is the one for you. Drop me a message if you want to take a look!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
