      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS. This specimen boasts a documented subframe reinforcement and a recent Rod Bearing service, ensuring mechanical longevity. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp engagement, while the factory limited-slip differential maintains optimal power delivery. The chassis remains taut with original suspension geometry intact, and the exterior retains its factory depth and luster. A mechanically flawless example for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 47500.0,
