    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional example of a 2017 BMW M2, presented in a condition that can only be described as showroom-fresh. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen inclement weather. The Long Beach Blue Metallic paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, free from stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings, thanks to a professional-grade ceramic coating applied last season. Inside, the cabin remains in factory-new condition; the black Dakota leather seats show zero bolster wear, and the carbon fiber trim is free of any delamination or scratches. Every switch, dial, and digital display functions with the crispness of a new car. Mechanically, this M2 is beyond reproach. It features a complete, documented service history from an authorized BMW dealership, with every fluid flush and inspection performed ahead of schedule. The undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork, showing no signs of corrosion or road grime. This sale includes both original keys, the factory window sticker, and all original owner\u2019s manuals. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands perfection, this vehicle offers a rare opportunity to own a modern classic that feels as though it just rolled off the assembly line.",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
